  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Santa needs your help collecting and delivering presents for christmas.  You have 3 days to save christmas or die trying. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>The plan is simple</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Assemble your elf crew with loot and aboard the sleigh</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Find presents in dark spooky places and make your escape before its too late</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Drop off presents and meet santa's delivery schedule</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Upgrades</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If you successfully complete santas delivery schedule you will be awarded with currency which you can use to buy new items</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Will You Help Santa Deliver?</strong> </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You'll travel collecting presents, discovering the horrors that lurk indoors.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Game Features</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fly to locations to find presents for santa</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Funny 1-4 player co-op gameplay</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Festive Horror</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Voice Chat</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Save Christmas (possibly)</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Santa needs your help collecting and delivering presents for christmas.  You have 3 days to save christmas or die trying. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>The plan is simple</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Assemble your elf crew with loot and aboard the sleigh</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Find presents in dark spooky places and make your escape before its too late</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Drop off presents and meet santa's delivery schedule</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Upgrades</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If you successfully complete santas delivery schedule you will be awarded with currency which you can use to buy new items</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Will You Help Santa Deliver?</strong> </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You'll travel collecting presents, discovering the horrors that lurk indoors.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Game Features</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fly to locations to find presents for santa</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Funny 1-4 player co-op gameplay</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Festive Horror</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Voice Chat</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Save Christmas (possibly)</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
